UC-01: Buyer Registration
Fields Required:
‚Ä¢	Full Name (min 2 chars)
‚Ä¢	Email (valid format)
‚Ä¢	Phone (Egyptian: 01 + 9 digits)
‚Ä¢	Password (min 8 chars)
‚Ä¢	Budget Range (number, SAR)
‚Ä¢	Preferred Locations (array, min 1)
‚Ä¢	Property Types (array, min 1)
‚Ä¢	Buying Intent (optional: Cash/Installment/Mortgage)
Flow:
1.	User fills form
2.	System validates (phone + email must be unique)
3.	System calculates score (see scoring section)
4.	Create account
5.	Redirect to /properties
Validation (Zod):
const buyerSchema = z.object({
  fullName: z.string().min(2, "Name too short"),
  email: z.string().email("Invalid email"),
  phone: z.string().regex(/^01[0-9]{9}$/, "Invalid Egyptian phone"),
  password: z.string().min(8, "Min 8 characters"),
  budget: z.number().positive("Budget required"),
  locations: z.array(z.string()).min(1, "Select location"),
  propertyTypes: z.array(z.string()).min(1, "Select property type"),
  buyingIntent: z.enum(['Cash', 'Installment', 'Mortgage']).optional()
})
