UC-09: Express Interest (Lead Creation)
Flow:
1.	Buyer clicks "I'm Interested" on property
2.	System checks matching rules (see matching engine below)
3.	If match succeeds: 
o	Create lead record
o	Add to marketer's "New Leads"
o	Add property to buyer's "My Interests"
4.	If match fails: 
o	Show message: "This property doesn't match your preferences"
Matching Engine Rules (ALL must be true):
function shouldCreateLead(buyer, property) {
  // Rule 1: Budget ¬±18%
  const budgetMin = buyer.budget * 0.82
  const budgetMax = buyer.budget * 1.18
  const budgetMatch = property.price >= budgetMin && property.price <= budgetMax
  
  // Rule 2: Location (exact or adjacent)
  const adjacentMap = {
    'New Cairo': ['Rehab', 'Madinaty'],
    '6th October': ['Sheikh Zayed', 'Beverly Hills'],
    'North Coast': ['Sidi Abdel Rahman', 'Hacienda']
  }
  const locationMatch = buyer.locations.includes(property.location) ||
    buyer.locations.some(loc => adjacentMap[loc]?.includes(property.location))
  
  // Rule 3: Type exact match
  const typeMatch = buyer.propertyTypes.includes(property.type)
  
  // Rule 4: Available
  const isAvailable = property.status === 'Available'
  
  return budgetMatch && locationMatch && typeMatch && isAvailable
}
